{"tid":763821,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人對有離心力既野好敏感","createTime":"2018-08-01T12:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T14:22:38.000Z","uid":196942,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"745aabcdac3ba0533974958b60312b9b717cadf2","tid":763821,"uid":196942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:16:57.000Z","msg":"如題.....<br />\n<br />\n我每次搭飛機前都會肚瀉 因為諗起起飛同搭飛機果時果啲氣流 而家大咗都還好啲 細個連飛機都唔敢搭 搞到對旅行呢樣野一啲興趣都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二樣係驚搭船 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 船呢樣野仲仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一企上去已經想走 個人會好不安 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比起飛機 我搭船會仲驚 係個海浮下又沉下咁 佢一起番上嚟果下我就勁想走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我唔搭得快船 會驚到手心出哂汗心跳好快個人崩緊咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有樣係搭車 有時的士或者紅van 勁快既話我會癲 好努力聽歌諗野比自己分心 但始終都係會focus番係個速度度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同人講又冇人明 點解我由細已經咁驚呢啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個個朋友成日走去玩機動遊戲 話好正好正 得我話唔去啦去咗都係睇動物睇其他野 我享受唔到當中既快樂 唔知有冇人有同感......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b2be8b8543234109f57a8d9f9691cd12739973","tid":763821,"uid":113178,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:22:06.000Z","msg":"係失重呀，唔係離心力"},{"pid":"f18f33940c1bb8d283e0fa6b52f19225808a6cd7","tid":763821,"uid":196942,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:25:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係失重呀，唔係離心力</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我由細到大都以為呢啲就係離心力 點解次次我一講啲人又唔糾正我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7040c10b17e929b5698143210bf96a41e78378b6","tid":763821,"uid":37233,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:32:44.000Z","msg":"我對依隻感覺係快感   會莫名地興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b83d84d96d7281c58e06d46023e4416bc0b9bf1","tid":763821,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:33:45.000Z","msg":"試試過山車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670b1420c0debb864e28379aa3f8fa1838da7023","tid":763821,"uid":157841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:34:38.000Z","msg":"海盜船先可以幫到你"},{"pid":"7318d6135e2e8e653d35c020a0c8c00699d3f944","tid":763821,"uid":196942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我對依隻感覺係快感   會莫名地興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好變態 我唔能夠理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f0f00783e4c287801aed47550145349d4d640a","tid":763821,"uid":196942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:38:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試試過山車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好耐以前膽粗粗試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一試就知原來真係冇辦法玩呢啲 你想我死呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ff7531bbb92eacca7a143266f32ad98e9d687b","tid":763821,"uid":156986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:39:30.000Z","msg":"細個搭船會驚到縮埋一舊，<br />\n大個要揸電單車扯到160以上先開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082e523c71e3e8339476d08fcb4f89a53c54168d","tid":763821,"uid":196942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:39:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>海盜船先可以幫到你</blockquote><br />\n比人捉過去玩海盜船一次仲要坐最尾果排 嚇到我瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  玩完行番出嚟果時隻腳仲震緊 跟住忍唔住喊左出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d8488f75a6a07b6df55fca69148dd2e4c060f1","tid":763821,"uid":196942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:40:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個搭船會驚到縮埋一舊，<br />\n大個要揸電單車扯到160以上先開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你係點突破 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc71e88d6786f47b128b65e38f691b2dfc83ab22","tid":763821,"uid":92023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:42:18.000Z","msg":"一樣 不過冇你咁敏感 <br />\n只要有chok嘅感覺 個心都好似離一離咁<br />\n試過搭過山車(諗住挑戰自己) 差啲pass out <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f17e11b7f7f3ef8d200a3b720ad82cc8935571e","tid":763821,"uid":75610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:42:37.000Z","msg":"渣架"},{"pid":"a601e105cadcfcd33eac28b7192be032328bf831","tid":763821,"uid":92023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"082e523c71e3e8339476d08fcb4f89a53c5416